I have this same problem and patched simple-scan like so:
```
diff --git a/src/page.vala b/src/page.vala
index 67c8010b..b1cfeee4 100644
--- a/src/page.vala
+++ b/src/page.vala
@@ -280,7 +280,7 @@ public class Page : Object

     private void parse_line (ScanLine line, int n, out bool size_changed)
     {
-        var line_number = line.number + n;
+        var line_number = int.min (line.number + n, scan_height - 1);

         /* Extend image if necessary */
         size_changed = false;
```

IMO, extending beyond the requested paper size is a misfeature that should be removed.

Hello Andre;
Ubuntu 24.04.1 LTS!
